org.spongepowered.api.item.inventory.property

Class SlotPos

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.spongepowered.api.item.inventory.property.AbstractInventoryProperty<String,com.flowpowered.math.vector.Vector2i>
      • org.spongepowered.api.item.inventory.property.SlotPos
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Property<?,?>>, Property<String,com.flowpowered.math.vector.Vector2i>, InventoryProperty<String,com.flowpowered.math.vector.Vector2i>

    public class SlotPos
extends AbstractInventoryProperty<String,com.flowpowered.math.vector.Vector2i>
    An inventory property which represents a position within a grid. Bear in mind that this property should be queried against the relevant parent, since a slot may have multiple parent inventories.
